  "short_description": "\"The Maze Survivor: First Entrants\" is a free online survival horror game that supports 1-5 players. You lost your memory and woke up in the center of a maze! The maze is full of monsters and traps. Find a way out of the maze through exploration, puzzle solving and cooperation!",
