  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"The Maze Survivor:First Entrants\" is the prologue to \"The Maze Survivor:The 9th Entrants\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is a limited space survival game that uniquely combines the characteristics of survival, horror, puzzle solving and maze adventure games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will play the role of the first batch of entrants into the maze. Compared with the ninth batch of entrants, you have fewer clues and more pressure to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will wake up in a wild jungle without any clues. Through the gaps in the leaves, they could see that they were surrounded by high walls. The walls open at dawn and close at night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/eb1312a9cbc813c2ebabdf1ecf11c424.poster.avif?t=1753970905\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/eb1312a9cbc813c2ebabdf1ecf11c424.webm?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/eb1312a9cbc813c2ebabdf1ecf11c424.mp4?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must try your best to collect enough supplies and establish their own stronghold in this relatively safe forest. When you are fully prepared, enter the maze full of unknown dangers, collect more important materials, solve complex puzzles, make marks, and try to extend your footprint as far as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/55dce729ffdd7fa0e3ebde893910c6bc.poster.avif?t=1753970905\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/55dce729ffdd7fa0e3ebde893910c6bc.webm?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/55dce729ffdd7fa0e3ebde893910c6bc.mp4?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But remember, unless you are fully prepared, escape to a safe area before nightfall!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/7b7d18ed9359da2196b9ab89b91a0a0d.poster.avif?t=1753970905\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/7b7d18ed9359da2196b9ab89b91a0a0d.webm?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/7b7d18ed9359da2196b9ab89b91a0a0d.mp4?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters will become more violent！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dangerous dark areas that will destroy your spirit! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And the visibility is extremely low, making it difficult for you to move! There seems to be a mysterious force behind the maze that affects your actions and constantly blocks your actions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go ahead and see if you can escape. If not, try to leave something behind for those who come after you.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"The Maze Survivor:First Entrants\" is the prologue to \"The Maze Survivor:The 9th Entrants\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is a limited space survival game that uniquely combines the characteristics of survival, horror, puzzle solving and maze adventure games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will play the role of the first batch of entrants into the maze. Compared with the ninth batch of entrants, you have fewer clues and more pressure to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will wake up in a wild jungle without any clues. Through the gaps in the leaves, they could see that they were surrounded by high walls. The walls open at dawn and close at night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/eb1312a9cbc813c2ebabdf1ecf11c424.poster.avif?t=1753970905\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/eb1312a9cbc813c2ebabdf1ecf11c424.webm?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/eb1312a9cbc813c2ebabdf1ecf11c424.mp4?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must try your best to collect enough supplies and establish their own stronghold in this relatively safe forest. When you are fully prepared, enter the maze full of unknown dangers, collect more important materials, solve complex puzzles, make marks, and try to extend your footprint as far as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/55dce729ffdd7fa0e3ebde893910c6bc.poster.avif?t=1753970905\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/55dce729ffdd7fa0e3ebde893910c6bc.webm?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/55dce729ffdd7fa0e3ebde893910c6bc.mp4?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But remember, unless you are fully prepared, escape to a safe area before nightfall!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/7b7d18ed9359da2196b9ab89b91a0a0d.poster.avif?t=1753970905\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/7b7d18ed9359da2196b9ab89b91a0a0d.webm?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322850/extras/7b7d18ed9359da2196b9ab89b91a0a0d.mp4?t=1753970905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters will become more violent！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dangerous dark areas that will destroy your spirit! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And the visibility is extremely low, making it difficult for you to move! There seems to be a mysterious force behind the maze that affects your actions and constantly blocks your actions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go ahead and see if you can escape. If not, try to leave something behind for those who come after you.</p>",
